ServiceListResponse[ExpectedIncome].description:
Represents a generic class for a service list response containing items of type T.
For a singular response data object use ServiceResponse.

data.description: Gets or sets the list of data of type T.

message.description: Gets or sets the message string with an initial value of an empty string.

chunk.description: Gets or sets the chunk value, with a default value of 1.

chunkSize.description: Gets or sets the size of the chunk.

totalChunks.description:
Gets or sets the total number of chunks.
Default value is 1.

totalRecordsInChunks.description: Gets or sets the total number of records in chunks.
